    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/472b89877d5aa1247424cf2d4b86ac22.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/472b89877d5aa1247424cf2d4b86ac22.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/472b89877d5aa1247424cf2d4b86ac22.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/b1be676d59a91d32f5fc1b70a42dd89f.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/fa14315a67891951aa72689c8a19ee56.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/fa14315a67891951aa72689c8a19ee56.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/fa14315a67891951aa72689c8a19ee56.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《希尔维亚物语》：一场精彩绝伦的冒险之旅</h2><br><strong>校长大人，您好！</strong><br><br>如果说生活是一部戏剧，那么我就是这部戏剧中《希尔维亚物语》游戏制作人的扮演者。今天，我非常荣幸地向您介绍这款新颖的沉浸式角色扮演游戏。<br><br><u>宏大的世界观，精彩的故事</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/d66262405e87cfcec1849b3853aff8f7.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/d66262405e87cfcec1849b3853aff8f7.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/d66262405e87cfcec1849b3853aff8f7.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《希尔维亚物语》的故事发生在“星渊之域”大陆上最强大的国家——“星宫帝国”。您将扮演凯尔维克军事学院的校长，在上任途中遭遇袭击，并得到不同伙伴的帮助，从而踏上妹子养成的道路。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/b1be676d59a91d32f5fc1b70a42dd89f.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=138 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/1681bf3b260675db42d2fb377c73327c.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/1681bf3b260675db42d2fb377c73327c.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/1681bf3b260675db42d2fb377c73327c.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >三位个性鲜明的女主角</h2><br>在《希尔维亚物语》中，您将邂逅三位个性鲜明的女主角，与她们展开一段段奇妙的冒险旅程。<br><br><u>一号妹子：汐儿</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/79952b6b590a019069b969ea6d9c7726.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/79952b6b590a019069b969ea6d9c7726.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/79952b6b590a019069b969ea6d9c7726.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>汐儿来自一个久经战乱的穷国“岚翔帝国”，从小失去双亲，吃百家饭长大的贫困女孩。由于您失去了记忆，所以由她以持律司工作人员的身份保护您前往首都“圣城-希尔维亚”上任。但她的持律司公职身份无法考证，途中请校长务必小心哦~<br><br><u>二号妹子：舞羽</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/af4484bab71f772ccc65a3aecc31c9eb.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/af4484bab71f772ccc65a3aecc31c9eb.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/af4484bab71f772ccc65a3aecc31c9eb.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>舞羽，黎明联邦舞蹈世家出身的天才舞者，失去父母后心怀复仇之念。金色服饰下隐藏着战士身份，以舞蹈为掩护积攒实力，一心谋求击败政变首脑叶强。风谷郡的舞娘生活磨练了她的意志，她以金色长裙和蛇鳞铠甲为武装，成为舞台与战场上的明星。在意外中失去记忆后，命运与主角的相遇将开启新的征程。<br><br><u>三号妹子：威雅</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/dfe4edd6c8291e5e4ee86180b08d46a8.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/dfe4edd6c8291e5e4ee86180b08d46a8.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/dfe4edd6c8291e5e4ee86180b08d46a8.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>威雅，出生于星宫帝国权贵家庭，曾过着奢华生活。但一次与主角一行的冲突成为她的转折点，意识到身份地位并非实力。为了守护国家，她决心加入军事学院，经历苦练和挫折，展现出顽强的意志和勇气。尽管曾多次面临失败和挑战，但她从未放弃。在一场突如其来的入侵中，虽然战斗中牺牲，但她的坚韧精神最终得到了神明的眷顾，重获新生。威雅的成长历程充满了艰辛与挑战，在主角的带领下凭借她的勇气和决心从一个被宠爱的少女到成为星之守护者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/a3548c447c836f92f97bec3b9a8bf379.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/a3548c447c836f92f97bec3b9a8bf379.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/a3548c447c836f92f97bec3b9a8bf379.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>精美的画面，沉浸式的体验<br><br>《希尔维亚物语》拥有精美的高清CG和立绘，以及大量精心制作的剧情动画，为您带来沉浸式的游戏体验。<br>目前游戏还在研发中，版本尚不稳定，待版本稳定后这里会上传具体实机画面哦，敬请期待~<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/36a572c3970fb82195a2b3353f718a7d.poster.avif?t=1769606018\" width=616 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/36a572c3970fb82195a2b3353f718a7d.webm?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181320/extras/36a572c3970fb82195a2b3353f718a7d.mp4?t=1769606018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>创新性的玩法，丰富的游戏内容<br><br>除了传统剧情以外，《希尔维亚物语》还融合了大量的丰富玩法，包括：<br><br>养成系统：培养您的女主角，提升她们的能力和属性。<br>战斗系统：体验紧张刺激的战斗，战胜强大的敌人。<br>解谜系统：运用您的智慧，解开各种谜题和机关。<br>收集系统：收集各种稀有物品，完成游戏目标。<br>《希尔维亚物语》，一款不容错过的精彩游戏！<br><br>校长大人，如果您是一位喜爱角色扮演游戏、剧情游戏、养成游戏、冒险游戏的玩家，那么《希尔维亚物语》绝对是您的不二之选！现在就下载游戏，开启您的奇妙冒险之旅吧！<br><br>《希尔维亚物语》，期待您的加入！<br><br>温馨提示：<br><br>游戏目前正在研发阶段，部分内容可能有所调整。<br>游戏最终解释权归6K6G Project所有。<br>祝您游戏愉快！",
